item.title: Flea Market
item.description: Theo Von is back with another solo episode of This Past Weekend chatting about back to school memories, the perils of riding the bus in his town, Morgan Wallen’s new haircut, his thoughts on the Barbie movie, terrible British superheroes, looking for love in the frozen food aisle, and more. He also responds to some of your voicemails. ------------------------------------------------ Tour Dates! https://theovon.com/tour New Merch: https://www.theovonstore... item.title: Speak Better English with Harry | Episode 444
item.description: In this podcast episode, you will learn 22 must-know speaking phrases for job interviews in English. Even in your native language, job interviews can be nerve-wracking; now, picture that anxiety when done in English. How to agree with the interviewer? What if you need to ask for clarification in English?  How to buy yourself some time? These useful speaking phrases will help you to prepare for your job interview in English...
